data.description: Pristine two story contemporary home on 5+acres! This home is move in ready with newer laminate floors throughout, large eat in kitchen  that walks out to maintenance free trex deck overlooking level backyard has abundant cabinetry and quartz countertops, center island, and pantry. Walk upstairs and enjoy judges paneling against the stairway that adds to the appeal. Spacious master bedroom w/en suite bath and walk in closet. Two additional nicely sized bedrooms and a den as well as laundry area are all on second floor. Two stall attached garage and two sheds are also offered. Situated on 5.6 acres of land, this is the perfect private home locale!
